The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Metro | Good Morning
                                                                                                                         3                                                                                      Good Morning
      Hello It's Sunday , October 10 , 2010                
	Go green     Walk/cycle/skate with others for a march from Victoria Memorial Hall to Raj Bhavan and back to voice your concern about climate change, 10am. Bring your non-motorised transport, and have fun.				 																																	   Join the Global Environment Action Day rally by RAIN from Chetla Park to Deshapriya Park to spread awareness about the citys increasing carbon footprint, 10am.   
	Birth anniversary    Attend a function to mark the 99th birth anniversary of Asoke Kumar Sarkar at MP Birla Planetarium, 5.15pm.         
	Music amp; poetry    Drop in at Sisir Mancha for a presentation of Tagore songs and poems by Sreekumar Chattopadhyay, Sraboni Bhattacharya and Amitava Bagchi, 5.30pm.        
	On stage    Enjoy the staging of Gorur Garir Headlight by Natasena at Girish Mancha, 6.30pm.        
	Eye on art    Check out Art In Life 2010, a group exhibition, at CIMA Gallery, 11am to 8pm.                                                                                                                                                  
